@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@json = application/json

### 1) Create without auth - should return 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "No auth category",
  "description": "This request should fail",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "#FF0000"
}

### 2) Register user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "email": "lab7@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3) Login user - cookies are stored by REST Client for the same host
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "email": "lab7@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4) Create with auth cookie - should work
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Food",
  "description": "Created after login",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "#00AAFF"
}

### 5) Read categories - should return the created item
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### 6) Refresh tokens - should issue new cookies
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh

### 7) Logout - should clear auth cookies
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
